attributes.title: the worst app i’ve ever downloaded
attributes.review: first of all, this app took 3.5 years to download. i 100% knew i would hate this app from the start and boy was my gut feeling correct. this has disappointed me more than i could even have imagined. this app spreads misinformation, has terrible design and taste, and made all of its users feel sick to their stomachs with disrespect and complete disregard for our app needs. i will never download an app like this again, and i hope other people open their eyes to how disgraceful this app is as well. if i could give this app 0 stars, i would. i am very close to getting rid of the app store and my apple phone in general and switching to android bc android phones would never allow such an app to exist. despicable.

attributes.title: My arm had to be amputated!
attributes.review: After I ate my peanut butter and jelly, my pencil walked up to me and told me how stupid my shoes looked! I was mortified! I never heard an object throw such delicious things at my butt. Then, the sky started to swallow my fruit loops, and I was triggered, so I ran into my mattress and threw my cabbages into its eye. The pinky toe was no match for me so I plugged my iPad in and went to sleep. The next thing I knew my arm was amputated! Terrible app.
